March, Hymn and Own Choice Test Piece Contest
Oxford Town Hall, Oxford, Oxfordshire, England, UK 23rd annual contest promoted by the City of Oxford Silver Band. No evening concert in this final year of the contest.
Open to non-championship bands.
Best instrumentalist: H. Stredwick, soprano cornet, Tredegar
Shipston are not listed in the programme, but are annotated by hand against the 3rd prize on the programme of the contest organiser.
